2. Project A: Educational and Design Criteria for e-content 
 develop a web based interface for e-content for 7 & 8 (Bengali, Math, Science, …) by each team consisting of 2 members playing all the expert roles..
 
Experts  including  coordinators,  team  leaders,  producers,  art  directors,  designers,  environment  compilers,  content  experts,  education  technologists,  education  psychologists,  education  sociologists,  scale  and  evaluation  experts  should  be  involved  in  the  production  of  e-content 

Steps
a) Determining the educational goals of the course (course’s general goal, partial 
goals, topic explanation, evaluation questions)
b) Determining  the  coverage  and  flow  required  to  accomplish  the  educational  
goal
c) Determining the evaluation scales
d) Producing the materials to be used in the content
e) Building the materials in order to produce educational results
f) Making changes according to the feedback on a trial version of the e-content


